Palʊla Igor Fiodorovitch Stravinsky kɛ mɩssɩ kʊm fenaɣ kiyakʊ 17 pɩnaɣ 1882  kɛ  Oraniyanbom  kɛ Rusii ɛjaɖ taa nɛ ɛsɩ ɖomaɣ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ looɖo wiye pɩnaɣ 1971 kɛ Niu Yɔrki tɛtʊ taa, Etazunii taa  ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 88. 

[[File:Igor Stravinsky, New York City (1946).png|thumb|Igor Stravinsky, New York City (1946)]]

Payaɣ ɛ-caa se Feodor Stravinski nɛ ɛlɛ ñaakɛ tanaʊ laɖʊ sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ kɛ Marinskɩ pɩlɩʊ taa. Igor Stravinsky kɛna pɩɣa naatozo ŋga pɩiya naanza taa nɛ paawɛ kʊñɔŋ sɔsɔʊ nakʊyʊ taa. Ɛ-ñɩma kaawɛ mʊzʊŋ nɛ wɛ piyena nɛ Igor Stravinsky ma se: « Ɛwɩlaɣ-m ɛ-sɔɔlɩm nɛ e-leleŋ kɛ alɩwaatʊ ndʊ pɩwɩɣ-m yɔ tiɖeke».

[[File:Passport chord.png|thumb|Passport chord]]

Ɛkɛ wendu luɖu, mʊsɩtɩnaa ñʊʊtʊ, piyano maɖʊ yaa hʊlʊyʊ. Ɛpɩsa ɛ-tɩ Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ tʊ pɩnaɣ 1934 nɛ Amerika tʊ pɩnaɣ 1945. E-wendu teu taa lɛ eeeteu kɩpɩndʊ ɛlɛ lɛɛlɛ taa wendu etu. Igor Fiodorovitch Stravinsky wɛ keteŋga kpeekpe taa  mba poluki wendu nɛ ɛya mba pakɩla ɖoŋ yaa keveŋga wɛnaʊ yɔ kɛ pɩnzɩ mɩnɩŋ XXe taa yɔ.

[[File:Igor Stravinsky - 3 Pieces for Clarinet Alone.ogg|thumb|Igor Stravinsky - 3 Pieces for Clarinet Alone]]
 
Ɛ-weendu ndu eluba yɔ, ɛ-tatasɩ nɛ ɛ-payɛ wandɩ ajɛyɛ kpeekpe nɛ waɣsɩ nɛ waɣsɩ waɣsɩ mbʊ pʊyɔɔ yɔ ɛlakasɩ e-wendu teu taa ɛ-wɛtʊ nɛ ɛ-payɛ wɛna ndɩ kpem. Pɩnzɩ 1920 taa ɛlɛɣzɩ ɛlakasɩ nɛ e-wendu teu wɛtʊ nɛ tiyele tɩnɩɣzɩna kɩpam lɩmaɣza kɩfaɖɛ nɛ esidiɣna sɔsɔ sɔnzɩ. Pɩnzɩ 1950 taa ɛlɛ Igor Fiodorovitch Stravinsky ɖaɣna lɛɣzɩ e-wendu teu wɛtʊ ɩñɩnʊ nɔmɔŋ weyi ɛtɩŋna nɛ e-wendu pɩzɩ nɛ tɩtɩŋ ɖama camɩyɛ lɔɔɔ yɔ.

